How to install external Nurbs++ Library for MBSim

1. Download: (http://sourceforge.net/projects/libnurbs/)
  
- download Nurbs++ library from http://sourceforge.net/projects/libnurbs/ and extract e.g. in ~/Nurbs/nurbs++-3.0.11/
- download patch (nurbs++-gcc4-patch.patch = nurbs++-3.0.11.1.patch and nurbs++-3.0.11.2.patch) and copy into ~/Nurbs/

2. Patchen

- change to ~/Nurbs/nurbs++-3.0.11
- use patch ("patch -p1 < nurbs++-3.0.11.1.patch")
- use patch ("patch -p1 < nurbs++-3.0.11.2.patch")

3. Installation

- configure project in ~/Nurbs/nurbs++-3.0.11/ ("./configure --prefix=~/MBSim/Install")
- compile and install project ("make install")

4. Possible Nurbs++ improvements

- virtual destructor
- plib_config.h <-> plib.h

